rows.name:
You see red tree from here? Is vivid
red that really pop out, brighter than
rest of all trees!

rows.label: tlk42200241_01_msg0002
rows.name: And it have special name: Saffronia!

rows.label: tlk42200241_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Harula move from Avaritia to
Fons Maim just to see Saffronia
tree every day!

rows.label: tlk42200241_01_msg0004
rows.name: Harula maybe bit obsessed with it...
